        Changed whether members can see who viewed the shared file or folder.

        Use newBuilder to create instances of this class without specifying values for all optional fields.

        Parameters:
        targetAssetIndex - Target asset position in the Assets list.
        newValue - New viewer info policy. Must not be null.
        originalFolderName - Original shared folder name.
        sharedFolderType - Shared folder type. Might be missing due to historical data gap.
        previousValue - Previous view info policy. Might be missing due to historical data gap.
